Interface Deployment.Update

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Appliable<Deployment>, Deployment.UpdateStages.WithMode, Deployment.UpdateStages.WithParameters, Deployment.UpdateStages.WithTemplate, Indexable
    Enclosing interface:
    Deployment

    public static interface Deployment.Update
extends Appliable<Deployment>, Deployment.UpdateStages.WithTemplate, Deployment.UpdateStages.WithParameters, Deployment.UpdateStages.WithMode
    The template for a deployment update operation, containing all the settings that can be modified.

    Call Appliable.apply() to apply the changes to the deployment in Azure.
